  13:../../libDaisy//src/util/WavPlayer.h ****  * At this time, this class only supports streaming of  16-bit WAV Files
  14:../../libDaisy//src/util/WavPlayer.h ****  * The output of this class will be in float converted from 16-bit integers
  15:../../libDaisy//src/util/WavPlayer.h ****  * and linearly interpolated for non-integer playback speeds.
  16:../../libDaisy//src/util/WavPlayer.h ****  *
