 301:../../libDaisy//src/util/WavPlayer.h ****     /** Stream Audio from disk at the current playback speed.
 302:../../libDaisy//src/util/WavPlayer.h ****      *
 303:../../libDaisy//src/util/WavPlayer.h ****      *    Each call to this will increment the playback position's
 304:../../libDaisy//src/util/WavPlayer.h ****      *  internal accumulator by the playback speed.
