 307:../../libDaisy//src/util/WavPlayer.h ****      *  audio samples.
 308:../../libDaisy//src/util/WavPlayer.h ****      *    Whenever the contents of the audio sample FIFO fall below
 309:../../libDaisy//src/util/WavPlayer.h ****      *  75% of it's capacity, a request is generated to refill it.
 310:../../libDaisy//src/util/WavPlayer.h ****      *    The maximum playback speed possible is limited to the following
 311:../../libDaisy//src/util/WavPlayer.h ****      *  factors:
 312:../../libDaisy//src/util/WavPlayer.h ****      *  - SD Card Bus-width
 313:../../libDaisy//src/util/WavPlayer.h ****      *  - SD Card Clock Speed
 314:../../libDaisy//src/util/WavPlayer.h ****      *  - workspace_bytes setting (consequently, transfer sizes)
 315:../../libDaisy//src/util/WavPlayer.h ****      *
 316:../../libDaisy//src/util/WavPlayer.h ****      *  It is possible to allow higher playback speeds, and improve
 317:../../libDaisy//src/util/WavPlayer.h ****      *  bandwidth by using higher workspace sizes, with the trade-offs
 318:../../libDaisy//src/util/WavPlayer.h ****      *  being memory, and latency with certain transactions.
 319:../../libDaisy//src/util/WavPlayer.h ****      *
 320:../../libDaisy//src/util/WavPlayer.h ****      *  @param samples buffer of floats to fill with audio samples from disk
 321:../../libDaisy//src/util/WavPlayer.h ****      *
 322:../../libDaisy//src/util/WavPlayer.h ****      *  @param num_channels number of channels provided to fill. This can be
 323:../../libDaisy//src/util/WavPlayer.h ****      *  different from the number of channels in the file.
 324:../../libDaisy//src/util/WavPlayer.h ****      */
